-- Real Madrid Signs Benfica's Argentina Midfielder Di Maria on Six-Year Deal
-- Alex Duff
-- 2010-06-28T19:43:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/real-madrid-signs-benfica-s-argentina-midfielder-di-maria-on-six-year-deal.html

          
          
             Real Madrid said it agreed to sign
Benfica’s Argentina midfielder Angel di Maria on a six-year
contract. Terms weren’t disclosed in a statement on the Spanish
team’s Web site.  
 Di Maria, 22, is playing at the World Cup with Argentina,
which beat Mexico 3-1 yesterday to reach the quarterfinals.  
          
          


  


        